    <item>
      <title>特朗普的加密项目购买与孙宇晨相关的代币</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/trump-s-crypto-project-buys-tokens-associated-with-justin-sun</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 的加密平台 World Liberty Financial 似乎已经将通过 Coinbase Global Inc. 推出的价值约 1000 万美元的所谓包装比特币 (wrapped Bitcoin) 兑换成了与项目顾问孙宇晨 (Justin Sun) 相关的类似代币。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/trump-s-crypto-project-buys-tokens-associated-with-justin-sun</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Dec 2024 18:07:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>自称比特币发明者的人在诉讼败诉后被判藐视法庭</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/self-proclaimed-bitcoin-inventor-found-in-contempt-of-court-after-lawsuit-loss</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一名谎称自己是比特币发明者的计算机科学家在一场惨痛的诉讼中败诉后，被伦敦一名法官裁定藐视法庭，并被判处缓刑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/self-proclaimed-bitcoin-inventor-found-in-contempt-of-court-after-lawsuit-loss</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Dec 2024 15:11:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>2024 年朝鲜黑客窃取了价值 13 亿美元的加密货币</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/north-korean-hackers-stole-record-1-3-billion-in-crypto-in-2024</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Chainalysis Inc. 称，与朝鲜有关的黑客今年从加密货币平台窃取的数据比以往任何时候都多，这表明其能力不断增强，研究人员认为这可能会威胁到美国国家安全。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/north-korean-hackers-stole-record-1-3-billion-in-crypto-in-2024</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Dec 2024 13:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
